Driving is a huge responsibility and Road Signs Game: Highway Code is a great tool to teach you all about highway exam, means, and rules to get your driver's license for cars or motorcycles, by improving your skills as you play the DMV permit test.

FEATURES:

Game to prepare you for DMV permit test;
Police agents;
Prohibition;
Mandatory;
Information;
Pictures with names.

With traffic volumes increasing since the 1930s, many countries have adopted the Highway Code with pictural signals or otherwise simplified and standardized their signals to overcome language barriers, and enhance traffic safety. As a result, such pictorial signs use symbols (often silhouettes) in place of words and are usually based on international protocols. Such signs were first developed in Europe, and have been adopted by most countries to varying degrees.

Knowing and updating your knowledge of road regulations is mandatory for all drivers, new and experienced in Highway Code. It illustrates and explains all the important highway code, and road markings for drivers, cyclists, and pedestrians.

Road signs have great importance in the driving process because knowing traffic rules and their meanings, make you a good driver. The game is designed to improve your signal driving skills for the DMV permit test.

Download and don't forget to share this amazing tool Traffic Game with your friends. 
Be careful when driving a car, remember - great responsibility.
Good luck on the roads!
